                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190526-50-off265 t18190526-50-crimeloc267"></join>. On the 10th of May, I saw the prisoner reach his hand inside the window, and take a book; he turned from the window, put it under his coat, and went away. I stopped him, he gave it to me, and begged my pardon - he was two doors from the shop.</p>
